 Syntax:  .write <message>

Results:  Enters a message on the message board of the room you are in.
          Selective hilites can be done with ^'s  One before the text you
          want to hilite in the message of another after. The number of
          ^'s you can use is unlimited.

  Notes:  Message lifetimes are currently approximately 6 days.

See also: read, wnote, suggest
